<view class="checkout-container"><view class="card-box address-card"><view class="card-header"><image class="icon" src="{{a}}" mode=""></image><text class="header-title">收货地址</text></view><view class="address-content"><view class="user-info"><text class="user-name">Endorphin</text></view><text class="address-detail">广东省深圳市龙岗区龙城街道龙翔大道2188号深圳信息职业技术大学</text><text class="user-phone">18512345678</text></view></view><view class="card-box summary-card"><view class="card-header"><image class="icon" src="{{b}}" mode=""></image><text class="header-title">订单详情</text></view><view class="summary-list"><view wx:for="{{c}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:key="d" class="summary-item"><text class="item-name">{{item.a}} x{{item.b}}</text><text class="item-price">￥{{item.c}}</text></view><view class="summary-item delivery-fee"><text class="item-name">配送费</text><text class="item-price">￥2.00</text></view></view></view><view class="card-box payment-card"><view class="card-header"><image class="icon" src="{{d}}" mode=""></image><text class="header-title">支付方式</text></view><view class="payment-list"><view wx:for="{{e}}" wx:for-item="pay" wx:key="d" class="{{['payment-item', pay.e && 'active']}}" bindtap="{{pay.f}}"><view class="pay-left"><image class="icon" src="{{pay.a}}" mode=""></image><text class="pay-name">{{pay.b}}</text></view><view class="radio-circle"><view wx:if="{{pay.c}}" class="inner-dot"></view></view></view></view></view><view class="footer-pay-bar"><view class="total-section"><text class="label">总金额</text><text class="amount">￥14.00</text></view><button class="pay-btn" bindtap="{{f}}">立即支付</button></view></view>